---
// src/pages/about.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Dazzle" description="Learn about Dazzle's consultation-first approach to diamond jewelry, transparent guidance, and custom design support.">
  <section class="about-us-hero container">
    <p class="about-kicker">About Dazzle</p>
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Diamond jewelry, chosen with clarity.</h1>
    <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Jeweler at work" class="about-hero-image" loading="eager" />
  </section>

  <section class="about-content container mt-4 mb-4">
    <div class="text-block">
      <h2>Consultation-first, not pressure-first</h2>
      <p>Dazzle is built around considered jewelry decisions. Whether you are exploring a ready piece, comparing diamond details, or planning a custom design, our role is to guide you through the choices that matter: design, certification, metal, budget, timeline, and long-term wearability.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-block">
      <h2>Transparency around quality</h2>
      <p>Diamond buying can feel opaque when every detail sounds technical. We focus on explaining the practical meaning of cut, clarity, color, carat, certification, and setting quality so you can make a confident decision instead of relying on guesswork.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-block">
      <h2>Custom design with clear steps</h2>
      <p>For custom rings and bespoke jewelry, we keep the process structured. We begin with your intent and references, discuss stone and metal options, clarify budget and timeline, and move forward only after the design direction feels right.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-cta">
      <h2>Planning a meaningful piece?</h2>
      <p>Start with a consultation or browse the current collection to understand the design language that fits you best.</p>
      <div class="about-actions">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn">Book a Consultation</a>
        <a href="/collections/" class="secondary-link">Browse Collections</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-us-hero {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffaf4 0%, #f0f0f0 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-kicker {
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    color: #A0907C;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-us-hero h1 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    color: #555;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .about-hero-image {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
  }

  .text-block,
  .about-cta {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(176, 160, 140, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .text-block h2,
  .about-cta h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #B0A08C;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .text-block p,
  .about-cta p {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-cta {
    background: #2b2624;
    color: #fffaf4;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-cta h2 {
    color: #fffaf4;
  }

  .about-cta p {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.4rem;
    color: rgba(255, 250, 244, 0.86);
  }

  .about-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .secondary-link {
    color: #f4dfbd;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
